    public class AQRRatingLocalServiceImpl
extends AQRRatingLocalServiceBaseImpl
    The implementation of the a q r rating local service.

    All custom service methods should be put in this class. Whenever methods are added, rerun ServiceBuilder to copy their definitions into the AQRRatingLocalService interface.

    This is a local service. Methods of this service will not have security checks based on the propagated JAAS credentials because this service can only be accessed from within the same VM.
